                <head>413. Telegram 1283 from Geneva<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d413fn1"
                        >Source: Department of State, Central Files, 611.93/12–1355. Secret; Limited
                        Distribution.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Geneva</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1955-12-13"
                            >December 13, 1955, 5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <pb facs="d413-1" n="1" type="facsimile" xml:id="d413-1"/>
                <p>1283. From <persName corresp="#p_JUA_1">Johnson</persName>. Reference: Paragraph
                    3 Department’s 1377.</p>
                <p>It is my understanding proposed recess to begin after meeting December 22.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_GFC_1">
                            <hi rend="strong">Gowen</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
